  - "What are the consequences of {action} in {context}?"
  - "Why is {procedure} preferred over {alternative_procedure}?"
  - "How does {equipment} improve {military_capability}?"
  - "What factors determine the success of {operation}?"
  - "Why must {safety_protocol} be followed during {activity}?"
  - "How does {weather_condition} affect {military_operation}?"
  - "What justifies the use of {tactic} in {scenario}?"

